Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:28.85,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,あのあのどんな色が　今ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:31.39,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,笑顔のホワイト　涙のブルー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:34.16,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,重ねてみたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:39.65,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,本日晴天なりっ　キャンパスに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:42.12,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,ミルクのアイス　ラムネごくん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:44.93,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,元気にカラートッピング
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:48.76,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,おーい！　ラブ描き·ぷりーす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:54.91,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,みんなの似顔絵コンテスト
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:02:02.12,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,よーし！　後で「ぷんっ」怒らないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:07.25,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,スイッチ押されたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:09.37,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,わっはっは～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:15.69,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,なんかいいキモチ　なればいいカンジ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:20.13,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,競争だ！　いち早くリンゴ食べよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:26.41,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,そうじゃないんだよ　躁でいいんだよ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:31.08,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,果物はモデルさん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:39.14,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,さあデッサンしましょうか　宿題だよん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:28.85,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,请问请问　现在是什么颜色呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:31.39,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容的白色　泪水的蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:34.16,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,将它们重叠在一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:39.65,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天气晴朗　外出郊游
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:42.12,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,进行冰牛奶弹珠汽水特训
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:44.93,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,代表精神的颜色正充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:48.76,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,喂－！　喜欢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:54.91,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,请来进行大家的肖像画素描比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:02:02.12,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,好－吧！　之后可别「砰」的一下就生气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:07.25,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,被人按下按钮时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:09.37,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:15.69,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得只要开心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:20.13,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛吧　看谁苹果吃得快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:26.41,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样　急躁起来好吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:31.08,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,水果便是模特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:39.14,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,来　开始素描吧　这是作业哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经早上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  所以才没有响的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  上学去了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么到这种地方来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.73,0:00:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:00:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃抵抗  赶快出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经完全被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,闹钟已经响过了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  上学去了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃抵抗  赶快出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经完全被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「2月13日  心灵和身体」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～  由乃变红了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是在发烧么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有体温计么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  38.2度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得请假在家休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不至于吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是出故障了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…今天真是冷死人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我尽快去准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:03:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃出故障了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你就安心休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事就手机联络哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,病情加重了就得去医院哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,离这里最近的医院在哪儿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  我们走了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保重身体\N注意保暖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁图斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可是很忙的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为闹钟没有响…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给  这是由乃的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得弄的更白一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是布鲁图斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是素描的基础么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  因为你穿成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好象只有脸颊开始变热了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真像个笨蛋一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于没有见到吉野屋老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就放假了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙只有在大家忙得焦头烂额的时候才会失踪…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许就在学校里的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以发现她的人请立即向我报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你们中有人迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那位在大冬天还穿着短袖的同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请以后多加注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校长生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他为什么会知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  变得更烫了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快些回教室去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被校长发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  小麦粉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果吉野屋老师在里面怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这我怎么好意思穿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:20.46,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,油漆未干\N注意防火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:20.46,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}易碎品注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:22.08,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（小麦面粉）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样行了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老师到哪里去了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一节课已经开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许真是出故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}thermostat　{\r}\N自动调温器？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正呼呼大睡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还很烫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  出了好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有些冷  忍耐一下哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  发现一颗痣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  这次是另一只
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「苹果…给我一个」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「不…不…不…不…我不干…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…老朽我可不理你」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:10.23,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：miyako和自己玩接龙呢…）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得在五年级的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔你在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自动调温器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  是来修这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那么热了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,故障修复了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  修复了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山吹地藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是见到了爸爸和妈妈就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.05,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（便利店）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没带钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（100日圆特价）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,100日圆特价
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得去告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,钱包我给扔哪儿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？智花？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是悄悄跑来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不会撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手机不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是智花发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是情人节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃的巧克力给谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都给不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发送
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:56.67,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（短信接收中）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  回得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是沙英学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好些了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在保健室拿了药我就回去
